page.title: 20The Domesday Survey-Credits
page.content: This survey of Cumwhinton and Wetheral and the surrounding area was carried out in June and July 1985 by the 4th.Year pupils of Cumwhinton Primary School.It is a rural school with 60 pupils covering an age range 4+-11+. Those taking part were:- E.K.Boyd Headmaster. Mrs.White A past parent. and the following pupils:- Simon Docherty (11) Alex Walton (11) Kevin Turnbull (11) Craig Wilson (10) Frances Pawson (11) Anna Comerford (11) Yvonne Lamb (11) Nicola Stevens (11) Alex Darling (10)
